[{"id": "example.txt:0", "text": "AI USB Assistant — Quick Guide\n\nThis is a portable AI assistant that runs entirely from a USB flash drive.\nIt uses Google Gemma 4 models with llama.cpp for local inference.\n\nSupported features:\n- Text chat with AI\n- Image recognition (vision)\n- Audio understanding\n- Thinking/reasoning mode\n- Local document search (RAG)\n\nModels:\n- Gemma 4 E2B: fast, light model, requires 4+ GB RAM\n- Gemma 4 E4B: smarter model, requires 8+ GB RAM", "source": "example.txt", "offset": 0}, {"id": "example.txt:1", "text": "emma 4 E2B: fast, light model, requires 4+ GB RAM\n- Gemma 4 E4B: smarter model, requires 8+ GB RAM\n\nRequirements:\n- Windows 10 or later\n- USB flash drive formatted as exFAT (not FAT32, because of 4 GB file limit)\n- Minimum 4 GB RAM\n\nHow to use:\n1. Plug in the USB flash drive\n2. Run Start_Windows.bat\n3. Wait for the model to load (15-60 seconds)\n4. Chat in the browser at http://127.0.0.1:8080", "source": "example.txt", "offset": 333}, {"id": "example.txt:2", "text": ".bat\n3. Wait for the model to load (15-60 seconds)\n4. Chat in the browser at http://127.0.0.1:8080\n\nTo use local document search:\n1. Place your documents (.txt, .md, .csv) in the data/docs folder\n2. Click \"Reindex Documents\" in the RAG panel (bottom-right corner)\n3. Enable \"Use local docs\" toggle\n4. Ask questions about your documents\n\nTips:\n- The USB must be exFAT formatted\n- No internet connection is needed\n- All data stays on your USB drive\n- Close the terminal window to stop the server", "source": "example.txt", "offset": 629}, {"id": "example.txt:3", "text": "n is needed\n- All data stays on your USB drive\n- Close the terminal window to stop the server", "source": "example.txt", "offset": 1029}, {"id": "tactics operation.txt:0", "text": "PROJECT: MINICLAW USB\n\nMiniClaw — это оффлайн AI ассистент, который работает с USB-флешки.\n\nОсновные характеристики:\n- Работает без интернета\n- Запускается в 1 клик\n- Использует локальные модели (Gemma, Qwen)\n- Может анализировать локальные файлы через RAG систему\n\nСекретный код проекта: 7429-ALPHA\n\nЭтот код нигде больше не используется и существует только в этом документе.", "source": "tactics operation.txt", "offset": 0}, {"id": "workflow-face-swap---move-ones-face-to-any-image-lErurUZwSEkY2mG7Lcmd-coco-openart.ai.json:0", "text": "{   \"last_node_id\": 165,   \"last_link_id\": 1697,   \"nodes\": [     {       \"id\": 119,       \"type\": \"ImageUpscaleWithModel\",       \"pos\": [         1580,         626       ],       \"size\": {         \"0\": 241.79998779296875,         \"1\": 46       },       \"flags\": {         \"collapsed\": false       },       \"order\": 10,       \"mode\": 0,       \"inputs\": [         {           \"name\": \"upscale_model\",           \"type\": \"UPSCALE_MODEL\",           \"link\": 1619,           \"slot_index\": 0         },", "source": "workflow-face-swap---move-ones-face-to-any-image-lErurUZwSEkY2mG7Lcmd-coco-openart.ai.json", "offset": 0}, {"id": "workflow-face-swap---move-ones-face-to-any-image-lErurUZwSEkY2mG7Lcmd-coco-openart.ai.json:1", "text": "l\",           \"type\": \"UPSCALE_MODEL\",           \"link\": 1619,           \"slot_index\": 0         },         {           \"name\": \"image\",           \"type\": \"IMAGE\",           \"link\": 1621         }       ],       \"outputs\": [         {           \"name\": \"IMAGE\",           \"type\": \"IMAGE\",           \"links\": [             1639           ],           \"shape\": 3,           \"slot_index\": 0         }       ],       \"properties\": {         \"Node name for S&R\": \"ImageUpscaleWithModel\"       }     },", "source": "workflow-face-swap---move-ones-face-to-any-image-lErurUZwSEkY2mG7Lcmd-coco-openart.ai.json", "offset": 396}, {"id": "workflow-face-swap---move-ones-face-to-any-image-lErurUZwSEkY2mG7Lcmd-coco-openart.ai.json:2", "text": "],       \"properties\": {         \"Node name for S&R\": \"ImageUpscaleWithModel\"       }     },